      "tags": [
        "Bounding",
        "Word Problems"
      ],
      "statement": "Nine copies of a certain pamphlet cost less than $\\$10.00$ while ten copies of the same pamphlet (at the same price) cost more than $\\$11.00$. How much does one copy of this pamphlet cost?",
